description: Legend BBQ is the story of three young men, a epic mobile food cabin and their food adventures. Their story tale began in the food being serve to their customers. The history of food has a tendency to travel with traditional flavors in every culture. For generations chicken, beef, and pork have been on top of the food chain for barbecues. The Legend BBQ has every great barbecue food story in every bite.
name: Legends BBQ
